<h4>Accessing the Page Setup Options Box in Classic Microsoft Excel</h4>


<p>In Classic Microsoft Excel, you click on <strong>File</strong> in the toolbar at the top of the spreadsheet. From the drop down File Menu that appears, click on <strong>Page Setup</strong>. The Page Setup Options Box will open. Using the Page Setup Options Box, you can customize the page margins for the spreadsheet.</p>


